Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.54,0:02:00.89,OPlrcJPN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}手放すのは怖いよね
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.96,0:02:06.58,OPlrcJPN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}でも待ち望んだ全ては
