Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.45,0:01:15.52,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}我為了不讓其毀壞而太過於珍惜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.63,0:01:21.44,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}今天我也輸入郵件
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.62,0:01:27.31,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}但又將其刪除
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.38,0:01:29.71,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}這樣的每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.83,0:01:32.88,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}將其打破的契機
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.91,0:01:36.72,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}為我帶來契機的指尖
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.77,0:01:40.70,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}用手心將其緊握
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.90,0:01:44.28,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}將現在改變
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.36,0:01:47.77,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}雖然也有苦痛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.84,0:01:51.64,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}即使將碎片全部收集齊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.80,0:01:54.84,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}也必須用自己的雙手將其指引
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.87,0:01:57.54,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}極其珍視的現在
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.54,0:02:00.89,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}我害怕將其失去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.96,0:02:06.58,OPlrcCHN,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(200,200)}但是我所希望的這一切
